
				ARESETTER v0.1
  
  By Martin Kluge, 2001
  Homepage: http://www.elxsi.de
  e-mail  : martin@elxsi.de
  Please use my public gpg key (key.pub) to encrypt important mails.
    -----------------------------------------------------------------

  ARESETTER is a simple program to reset network connections.
  It works by sniffing the network traffic for three-way-handshakes
  and by constructing TCP packets with the RST flag and the right
  sequence number.

  ARESETTER comes under the GPL (see COPYING for more details).
    -----------------------------------------------------------------
								Martin Kluge
  
